text: Ibrahima Fall Faye (born 10 January 1997) is a Senegalese professional basketball player for the Antwerp Giants of the Pro Basketball League (PBL). ==Professional career== Fall Faye played in the youth teams of Élan Chalon.. He played 9 matches in the LNB Pro A with during the 2016–17 season., as well as three matches in the FIBA Europe Cup and one in the 2017 Leaders Cup. In April 2018, he declared for the 2018 NBA draft.
